dcterms:description: The ACL18 StockNet dataset contains the historical prices of 88 high trade volume stocks from the U.S. market, which represents the top 8-10 stocks in capital size across 9 major industries. The duration of data ranges between 01/01/2014 to 01/01/2017.
dcterms:title: ACL18 StockNet dataset

dcterms:description: The U.S. stock data is an updated extension of the ACL18 StockNet dataset, which includes data collected from 01/01/2017 to 01/01/2023, taking the latest top 10 stocks from the 11 major industries, resulting in a total of 110 stocks.
dcterms:title: U.S. stock data (updated from ACL18 StockNet dataset)
